&lt;p&gt;Transposed Convolution/ fractionally-strided / deconvolution&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;转置卷积不是卷积的逆运算&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;N.B.: Blue maps are inputs, and cyan maps are outputs.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
